## Brownfield Sites assisted by the state of Colorado (webmap and hosted feature later)

I've never worked with geojson before, but here is the link to the dataset showing brownfields in the state: 

https://services3.arcgis.com/66aUo8zsujfVXRIT/ArcGIS/rest/services/CDPHE_Brownfield/FeatureServer/0?f=pjson

As well as a link to other Environmental maps and GIS data that might be of use through the state Department of Public Health and the Environment: 

https://cdphe.colorado.gov/hm-gis-data

